metadata.name: ActivityPub::ProcessAccountService when account is not suspended queues suspension worker

sql_query.sql: SELECT "domain_blocks".* FROM "domain_blocks" WHERE "domain_blocks"."domain" IN ($1, $2) ORDER BY char_length(domain) desc LIMIT $3

sql_query.sql: SELECT "follows".* FROM "follows" WHERE "follows"."target_account_id" = $1 AND "follows"."account_id" IN (SELECT "accounts"."id" FROM "accounts" WHERE "accounts"."domain" IS NULL) ORDER BY "follows"."id" ASC LIMIT $2

SELECT a.attname
  FROM (
         SELECT indrelid, indkey, generate_subscripts(indkey, 1) idx
           FROM pg_index
          WHERE indrelid = '"tombstones"'::regclass
            AND indisprimary
       ) i
  JOIN pg_attribute a
    ON a.attrelid = i.indrelid
   AND a.attnum = i.indkey[i.idx]
 ORDER BY i.idx
